The use of Bayesian optimization and surrogate models also suggests a connection to the subfield of machine learning. The paper also discusses the handling of constraints, which is a topic in control systems and optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The use of optimization techniques and the handling of constraints also suggest a connection to the subfield of control systems, which is covered by cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the use of surrogate models and the analysis of convergence suggest a connection to the subfield of data structures and algorithms, which is covered by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
